headline: Q2 Earnings Highs And Lows: Ross Stores (NASDAQ:ROST) Vs The Rest Of The Discount Retailer Stocks
summary: The end of an earnings season can be a great time to discover new stocks and assess how companies are handling the current business environment. Let’s take a look at how Ross Stores (NASDAQ:ROST) and the rest of the discount retailer stocks fared in Q2.
